        <mxCell id="note-scope" value="&lt;b&gt;Diagram Scope&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;The source defines formal relationships only for the five entity classes. Boundary, control, business-logic, service, and proxy classes are included here as categorized notes to preserve the full static model without inventing unsupported UML associations." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;size=15;fillColor=#f8fafc;strokeColor=#94a3b8;fontColor=#0f172a;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
